+<h2 style="margin-top:32px; border-bottom-color:#555;">Addressed via Reimagining the Unified Builder</h2>
+<p class="chapter-sub">The following initiatives are part of the <a href="unified-builder-roadmap.html">Mailchimp Unified Builder FY27 roadmap</a>. They directly enhance automation flows through the shared editor and content layer, and are tracked under the Unified Builder strategy rather than duplicated here.</p>
