+    <tr><td class="init-cell">Brand Kit integration + generative copy in journeys</td><td>Brand Kit (colors, typography, voice) auto-applied to AI-generated flow emails; in-canvas inline rewrite, tone, length, and CTA generation; AI subject-line generator in flow email steps. <strong>$11,485/mo</strong> HVC exposure.</td><td>AI-Powered Builder &amp; Accelerated Time to Value (P3)</td></tr>
+    <tr><td class="init-cell">AI product recommendation blocks in flow messages</td><td>Drag-in dynamic content blocks (&ldquo;next best product,&rdquo; &ldquo;complete the look&rdquo;) that auto-populate per-recipient inside any flow email or SMS. Matches Klaviyo&rsquo;s productized AI rec story.</td><td>AI-Powered Builder &amp; Accelerated Time to Value (P3)</td></tr>
